---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="fr"
  title="Nouveaut&eacute;s - AIVancePro | Changelog et mises &agrave; jour"
  description="D&eacute;couvrez les derni&egrave;res mises &agrave; jour d'AIVancePro. Nouvelles fonctionnalit&eacute;s, am&eacute;liorations et corrections pour votre coach fitness IA."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/nouveautes/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/nouveautes/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/changelog/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/neuigkeiten/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .changelog-hero {
          padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
          text-align: center;
          background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      }
      .changelog-hero h1 {
          font-size: 3rem;
          font-weight: 900;
          letter-spacing: -0.03em;
          color: var(--gray-900);
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .changelog-hero h1 .gradient {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          -webkit-background-clip: text;
          -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
          background-clip: text;
      }
      .changelog-hero p {
          font-size: 1.15rem;
          color: var(--gray-500);
          max-width: 550px;
          margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .timeline-section {
          padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
          max-width: 800px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          position: relative;
      }
      .timeline-line {
          position: absolute;
          left: 28px;
          top: 3rem;
          bottom: 5rem;
          width: 2px;
          background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--blue), var(--purple), var(--gray-200));
          border-radius: 2px;
      }
      .timeline-item {
          position: relative;
          padding-left: 68px;
          margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }
      .timeline-dot {
          position: absolute;
          left: 20px;
          top: 1.8rem;
          width: 18px;
          height: 18px;
          border-radius: 50%;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          border: 3px solid var(--bg);
          box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
          z-index: 1;
      }
      .timeline-card {
          background: var(--bg-card);
          border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
          border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
          border-radius: 16px;
          padding: 2rem;
          transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .timeline-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-2px);
          box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .version-header {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 1rem;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .version-badge {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          color: var(--white);
          font-size: 0.8rem;
          font-weight: 700;
          padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
          border-radius: 50px;
          letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }
      .version-date {
          font-size: 0.85rem;
          color: var(--gray-500);
          font-weight: 500;
      }
      .version-title {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          font-weight: 800;
          color: var(--gray-900);
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .changelog-list {
          list-style: none;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 0.6rem;
      }
      .changelog-list li {
          display: flex;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 0.6rem;
          font-size: 0.92rem;
          color: var(--gray-700);
          line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .changelog-list li svg {
          width: 18px;
          height: 18px;
          color: var(--blue);
          flex-shrink: 0;
          margin-top: 2px;
      }
      .changelog-cta {
          text-align: center;
          padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
          background: var(--bg-card);
          border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      }
      .changelog-cta h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
          font-weight: 800;
          color: var(--gray-900);
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .changelog-cta p {
          font-size: 1.05rem;
          color: var(--gray-500);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          max-width: 500px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
      }
      .btn-cta {
          display: inline-block;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          color: var(--white);
          font-size: 0.95rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
          border-radius: 12px;
          text-decoration: none;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
          transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .btn-cta:hover {
          opacity: 0.92;
          transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .changelog-hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
          .timeline-line { left: 18px; }
          .timeline-dot { left: 10px; top: 1.6rem; width: 16px; height: 16px; }
          .timeline-item { padding-left: 48px; }
          .timeline-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
          .version-title { font-size: 1.1rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="changelog-hero">
        <h1>Les <span class="gradient">nouveaut&eacute;s</span></h1>
        <p>D&eacute;couvrez les derni&egrave;res mises &agrave; jour et am&eacute;liorations d'AIVancePro.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <section class="timeline-section">
        <div class="timeline-line"></div>

        <!-- Version 2.1 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
                <div class="version-header">
                    <span class="version-badge">v2.1</span>
                    <span class="version-date">Mars 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="version-title">S&eacute;curit&eacute; &amp; stabilit&eacute;</div>
                <ul class="changelog-list">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Nouveau syst&egrave;me de blocage et signalement des utilisateurs</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Permissions cam&eacute;ra iOS pour iPad</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Nouvelles ic&ocirc;nes Android</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Am&eacute;liorations des notifications et recherche utilisateurs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Version 2.0 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
                <div class="version-header">
                    <span class="version-badge">v2.0</span>
                    <span class="version-date">F&eacute;vrier 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="version-title">Refonte compl&egrave;te</div>
                <ul class="changelog-list">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Migration compl&egrave;te vers Supabase (auth, DB, realtime)</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Nouveau coach IA avec streaming OpenAI</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Upload d'images via Cloudinary</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Push notifications OneSignal</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Syst&egrave;me de pr&eacute;sence en temps r&eacute;el</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Version 1.5 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
                <div class="version-header">
                    <span class="version-badge">v1.5</span>
                    <span class="version-date">Janvier 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="version-title">Communaut&eacute; &amp; social</div>
                <ul class="changelog-list">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Page communaut&eacute; avec feed, groupes, d&eacute;fis</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Syst&egrave;me de messagerie priv&eacute;e</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Leaderboards et classements</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Partage social des performances</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Version 1.0 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
                <div class="version-header">
                    <span class="version-badge">v1.0</span>
                    <span class="version-date">D&eacute;cembre 2025</span>
                </div>
                <div class="version-title">Lancement initial</div>
                <ul class="changelog-list">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Lancement initial iOS &amp; Android</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Coach IA conversationnel</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>+240 exercices avec vid&eacute;os</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Suivi de progression avec graphiques</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Syst&egrave;me de templates</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Timer de repos int&eacute;gr&eacute;</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>3 plans : Gratuit, Pro (4,99&euro;/mois), Elite (7,99&euro;/mois)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="changelog-cta">
        <h2>Pr&ecirc;t &agrave; essayer ?</h2>
        <p>T&eacute;l&eacute;chargez AIVancePro et profitez de toutes ces fonctionnalit&eacute;s d&egrave;s maintenant.</p>
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/fr/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">T&eacute;l&eacute;charger l'app</a>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
